teo.isgci.problem

Enum Complexity

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Complexity>
      • teo.isgci.problem.Complexity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Complexity>

    public enum Complexity
extends java.lang.Enum<Complexity>
    Represents complexity classes like Linear, P, NPC, coNPC and Unknown. Use only the defined comparison methods, the enum compareTo does not give a complexity comparison. The betterThan and betterOrEqual compare as LIN < P < GIC < NPC,NPH,CONPC. betterThan with other complexities is undefined.
